Class QueryDqlObjectWebfsService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.rogetmf.webfs.service.AbstractWebfsService
      • com.emc.rogetmf.webfs.service.QueryDqlObjectWebfsService

  • public class QueryDqlObjectWebfsService
extends AbstractWebfsService
    Service providing methods used to initiate and process D2cQueryDql objects based on D2QueryFormConfig templates with FreeMarker syntax used in DQL
    Author:
    Krzysztof Jurkowski

    • Method Detail

      • initQueryDqlObject

        public java.lang.String initQueryDqlObject(com.documentum.fc.client.IDfPersistentObject queryFormObject)
                                    throws com.documentum.fc.common.DfException,
                                           com.emc.d2fs.exceptions.D2fsException,
                                           java.lang.NullPointerException
        Initializes a D2cQueryDql object for a given Public search. FreeMarker DQL template from the D2QueryFormConfig Query form is copied to the DQL attribute of D2cQueryDql object. The D2cQueryDql object is reused afterwards, so that each user has no more than on D2cQueryDql object in the repository.
        Parameters:
        queryFormObject - Query form from which the FreeMarker DQL template is to be copied
        Returns:
        Object ID of the initialized D2cQueryDql object.
        Throws:
        com.documentum.fc.common.DfException
        com.emc.d2fs.exceptions.D2fsException
        java.lang.NullPointerException - Occurs if passed QueryFormConfig object is null

      • processQueryDqlObject

        public java.lang.String processQueryDqlObject(java.lang.String propertyPageName,
                                     java.util.Hashtable<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> attributesHashtable)
                                       throws com.documentum.fc.common.DfException,
                                              com.emc.d2fs.exceptions.D2fsException,
                                              java.io.IOException,
                                              freemarker.template.TemplateException,
                                              java.lang.NullPointerException
        Processes the FreeMarker DQL template stored in the initialized D2cQueryDql object. Resulting DQL is saved back in the D2cQueryDql object.
        Parameters:
        attributesHashtable - Contains pairs - the name of the parameter in the FreeMarker DQL template and the value of the parameter provided by the user
        Returns:
        Object ID of the processed D2cQueryDql object
        Throws:
        com.documentum.fc.common.DfException
        com.emc.d2fs.exceptions.D2fsException
        freemarker.template.TemplateException - Occurs if the FreeMarker DQL template cannot be processed
        java.io.IOException
        java.lang.NullPointerException - Occurs if no initialized D2cQueryDql object can be found for the session user

      • getQueryDqlObjectForQuickSearch

        public java.lang.String getQueryDqlObjectForQuickSearch(java.lang.String quickSearchTerm)
                                                 throws java.lang.NullPointerException,
                                                        com.documentum.fc.common.DfException,
                                                        com.emc.d2fs.exceptions.D2fsException,
                                                        java.io.IOException,
                                                        freemarker.template.TemplateException
        Prepares a D2cQueryDql object for a Quick search. It requires a ROG_QUICK_SEARCH Query form stored in the repository. The query form must contain a FreeMarker DQL template of the DQL executed by the Quick search.
        Parameters:
        quickSearchTerm - Quick search term value
        Returns:
        Object ID of the D2cQueryDql object
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - Occurs if ROG_QUICK_SEARCH Query form was not found
        com.emc.d2fs.exceptions.D2fsException
        com.documentum.fc.common.DfException
        java.io.IOException
        freemarker.template.TemplateException - Occurs if the FreeMarker DQL template cannot be processed
